rows.label: tlk43700149_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I was convinced we were
going to war, but they
called the whole thing off...

rows.label: tlk43700149_03_msg0002
rows.name:
It'll be a bitter pill to
swallow for Superbia, but
more importantly, for Acedia.

rows.label: tlk43700149_03_msg0003
rows.name:
You really think they'll let off those
guys in the buffer zone after digging
up something crazy like that?

rows.label: tlk43700149_03_msg0004
rows.name:
The army and mercs here were all
riled up and ready for action, too.

rows.label: tlk43700149_03_msg0005
rows.name:
If the queen had given the
word, we'd have been down on
them like a ton of bricks.
